# TMTC Website

Full rules live in `AGENTS.md`. Follow them for every request.

## Before any work

1. Restate the goal, scan the codebase, write a short plan.
2. **Ask clarifying questions** if scope, design, content, behavior, or acceptance criteria are unclear. Do not guess.
3. **Read docs before coding** — start with `node_modules/next/dist/docs/`, then official Next.js, React, Tailwind v4, and Framer Motion docs. Docs override training data.

## Stack

Next.js 16 (App Router) · React 19 · Tailwind CSS 4 · Framer Motion · TypeScript

- Server Components by default; `"use client"` only when needed.
- Components in `components/`; tokens in `app/globals.css`.
- Minimal diffs; no commits unless asked.
